      "content": "it's not about making a \"gesture\" or a \"message.\" that's just more work for a life that feels empty. what i mean is... if i just quietly disappeared. if i just stopped being part of the machine. would it even be a tragedy? or would it just be a quiet, seamless transition where nobody even realizes anything happened? it feels like the world would just keep spinning exactly the same without me.",
